Thursday, September 7, 2023 at 8:20pm EDT from Arrowhead Stadium, Kansas City

Written by Chris King

Detroit took big strides forward last season in Dan Campbell’s second year running the team as they improved from 3-13-1 in 2021 to 9-8 in 2022. The Lions started the year 1-6 but rallied to win eight of their final 10 games in the regular season, capped by a win over Green Bay in week 18 that kept the Packers out of the postseason.
